import react from "react";
import { CardGroup, Card } from "react-bootstrap";
import card1 from "./img/card1.png";
import card2 from "./img/card2.png";
import card3 from "./img/card3.png";

const content = () => {
  return (
    <CardGroup id="content">
      <Card>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={card1} />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Bali Trip Planner</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>Planning a trip to Bali? Build a trip using Bali trip planner now!</Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
        <Card.Footer>
          <small href="#" class="btn btn-dark">
            Read more
          </small>
        </Card.Footer>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={card2} />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Labuan Bajo</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>A trip to Labuan Bajo, an idyllic fishing village at the northwestern tip of Flores, etc.</Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
        <Card.Footer>
          <small href="#" class="btn btn-dark">
            Read more
          </small>
        </Card.Footer>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={card3} />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title>Traditional Food</Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>What's the best food in Yogyakarta? These are 17 most popular local traditional dishes.</Card.Text>
        </Card.Body>
        <Card.Footer>
          <small href="#" class="btn btn-dark">
            Read more
          </small>
        </Card.Footer>
      </Card>
    </CardGroup>
  );
};

export default content;
